title: Did the Maasai people donate 14 cows to the United States after 9/11?
subtitle: A common idea on the Internet that members of the Maasai tribe donated cows to the United States after the terrorist attacks of 11 September 2001 is accurate.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The Maasai have donated 14 cows to the United States after 9/11.
